    The main driver of the program
    IR
    The IR class is in charge of running an Instant Runoff election and outputting any results to the audit file, media report, and display.

    IR Manual Unit Tests These tests are those which has some form of manual component for the tester.
    IRSystemTest
    IR System unit Tests These tests are fully automatic and do not require any manual steps.
    IRTest
    IR Unit Tests
    IRTestHelpers
    Helper functions used by IR Test
    OPL
    The OPL class is in charge of running an Open Party List election and outputting any results to the audit file, media report, and display.
    OPLManualTest
    OPL Manual Unit Tests These tests are those which has some form of manual component for the tester.
    OPLSystemTest
    OPL System unit Tests These tests are fully automatic and do not require any manual steps.
    OPLTest
    OPL Unit Tests These tests are fully automatic and do not require any manual steps.
    OPLTestHelpers
    Helper functions used by both OPLTest and OPLManualTest
    Party
    Party class represents the parties participating in the election.
    PartyTest
    Party Class Unit Tests These tests are fully automatic and do not require any manual steps.
    PO
    Dummy PO class that just stores the information for PO but doesn't actually run any solving algorithm.
    POTest
    Tests for the PO election type.
